{"tid":1814664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］不如搞返個感謝勇武手足集氣大會","createTime":"2020-01-07T04:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T06:30:57.000Z","uid":12583,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e2b066645948d6e979668c1064aba4a8f4167f","tid":1814664,"uid":12583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:10:08.000Z","msg":"近排有股勇武小隊解散潮<br />\n我上一個Post都講咗自己嘅說法<br />\n係到就廢事詳敍<br />\n但我相信大家都有個共識係<br />\n有好多少上網/年紀較大嘅手足嘅「不捉鬼」意識比較薄弱<br />\n近來的而且確有好多手足，尤其係勇武<br />\n對呢排嘅運動風潮比較灰心<br />\n而見到有人話咩「真勇武一定唔會退場」呢啲不知所謂啲論調就更係眼火爆<br />\n其實我地唔應該將其他人嘅付出當係老俸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我地不如搞返個集會<br />\n多謝一眾勇武同其他手足嘅付出<br />\n令佢地知道大家冇放棄到<br />\n同時唔會隨便割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外集會期間大家可以多做文宣<br />\n將不捉鬼嘅意識宣揚出去<br />\n去REACH更多群體嘅人<br />\n一人行多步 做實事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我希望集會真係可以凝聚到手足嘅心<br />\n鼓勵大家繼續努力<br />\n為同路人打氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f882367e9dbc27962aa8df76b083a41d5f7813","tid":1814664,"uid":258696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:11:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Up<br />\n支持勇武行動<br />\n阻礙左中國肺炎散播</span>"},{"pid":"5b0662a0307068e5d2767cfb08f78205f13db74e","tid":1814664,"uid":12583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:11:16.000Z","msg":"又或者我地可以係現有<br />\n並且係將舉行嘅集會<br />\n去宣揚不捉鬼嘅訊息<br />\n同時為手足們打棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a7c42f8b479cd7d3ba5197788175f384f33aad","tid":1814664,"uid":12583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:12:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又或者我地可以係現有<br />\n並且係將舉行嘅集會<br />\n去宣揚不捉鬼嘅訊息<br />\n同時為手足們打<span style=\"color: red;\">氣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自膠 打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆街打速成都可以打錯<br />\n一時手殘sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa8ab9c2a36e5b274965b2124f5a94bc9b5327e","tid":1814664,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:13:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n1月8日 星期三<br />\n齊齊去幫襯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1813301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1813301</a><br />\n</div></span>"},{"pid":"51142e3aebd4c3d04c57fbd53d6a0141b6a68a1e","tid":1814664,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:13:21.000Z","msg":"咁樣標籤和理非/勇武好易有反效果，角色定形"},{"pid":"cbb68b4e1cbe0f1151b894be64f18e348a0e9ec3","tid":1814664,"uid":83910,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:14:04.000Z","msg":"&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n遊行集會請幫手叫新口號<br />\n「手足好珍貴<br />\n    唔好再捉鬼」"},{"pid":"21cdd290669f8df425f93cd535d27b7f57558799","tid":1814664,"uid":12583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51142e3aebd4c3d04c57fbd53d6a0141b6a68a1e","tid":1814664,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:13:21.000Z","msg":"咁樣標籤和理非/勇武好易有反效果，角色定形"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:14:57.000Z","msg":"多謝手足意見<br />\n或者改做手足集氣大會？"},{"pid":"6307773b9b59ccf8d6e756f5c0baf37cc84551fc","tid":1814664,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51142e3aebd4c3d04c57fbd53d6a0141b6a68a1e","tid":1814664,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:13:21.000Z","msg":"咁樣標籤和理非/勇武好易有反效果，角色定形"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:15:02.000Z","msg":"根本和勇不分，點解要加標籤"},{"pid":"0cc67fd763ea38db38c17ff5b56f93e18d9c41e9","tid":1814664,"uid":12583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbb68b4e1cbe0f1151b894be64f18e348a0e9ec3","tid":1814664,"ui